# Cursor Rules for Toddler Audio Jukebox

# UI/UX Philosophy
- TARGETS: Buttons must be at least 100dp x 100dp for toddler coordination.
- DISTRACTIONS: No search bars, no progress bars, keep the UI simple and focused on the task.

# Technical Preferences
- Use Jetpack Compose for all UI.
- Use Coil for image loading with crossfade enabled.
- Use Media3 for all audio logic.
- Ensure all file access uses the Scoped Storage / Storage Access Framework (SAF) approach for Android 13+.

# Error Handling
- If a folder has no image, use a high-contrast colorful placeholder icon, never a text "Error" message.